
To use the images.json file to upload images, edit images.json
to point to your 8b grayscale file(s), then run

   ../../soc/bin/litex_term  --images images.json --speed 3686400 /dev/ttyUSB2



To create a 96x96 8b grayscale file from an arbitrary image "image.jpg", use


   convert -resize 96x96\!  -grayscale average -depth 8 image.jpg image.gray


The escaped "!" is necessary to force the 1:1 aspect ration.






